": 6842}]}, {\"sentence\": \"People like Purchase, Norris, Ikeji, Campbell and the rest of the British athletes who thought they would have the chance to compete in Paris but will instead be watching on television from afar.\", \"from\": 6844, \"to\": 7039, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6881, \"end\": 6889, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Campbell\", \"score\": 0.9999999999936335, \"rank\": 6.427166431686893e-12, \"text\": \"Campbell\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Campbell\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Campbell\"}, {\"begin\": 6910, \"end\": 6917, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9721789442531585, \"rank\": 0.01892202448363756, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 6980, \"end\": 6985, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.103161333652813e-14, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"People\", \"from\": 6844, \"to\": 6850}, {\"ngram\": \"Purchase\", \"from\": 6856, \"to\": 6864}, {\"ngram\": \"Norris\", \"from\": 6866, \"to\": 6872}, {\"ngram\": \"Ikeji\", \"from\": 6874, \"to\": 6879}, {\"ngram\": \"the rest\", \"from\": 6894, \"to\": 6902}, {\"ngram\": \"the chance\", \"from\": 6955, \"to\": 6965}, {\"ngram\": \"television\", \"from\": 7018, \"to\": 7028}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What would have become of Thompson if he had been put in the same position of not competing at those Montreal Games as a teenager in 1976?\", \"from\": 7041, \"to\": 7179, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7067, \"end\": 7075, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Klay_Thompson\", \"score\": 0.9945784835285224, \"rank\": 0.005451069534804722, \"text\": \"Thompson\", \"types\":